Paul D. Weiner, DPM

Welcome! Since 1996, Dr. Paul Weiner has been working with patients to provide the best podiatric care for patients in the Vallejo, CA area. Dr. Weiner's experience in podiatry is coupled with genuine concern for his patients. All our staff is dedicated to your comfort and prompt attention as well. Our goal is to help you maintain healthy feet.
This web site provides you with an overview of our practice and the field of podiatry. As you navigate the site, you'll find information about Dr. Weiner 's practice philosophy, our office location, insurance policies, and appointment scheduling procedures. Please browse the site at your convenience and feel free to contact us with any questions.
You'll find a lot of valuable information on the web site about foot problems, diagnoses and treatments. We believe informed patients are better prepared to make decisions about their health and well being. We encourage you to review this information to help you understand any health concerns you may face.
 
 
 
  








	Paul D. Weiner, DPM is a podiatrist focusing on podiatric procedures such as bunions, heel spurs, and hammertoes. Paul D. Weiner, DPM is a Board Certified Podiatrist in the state of California.
	Podiatrist - Vallejo, Weiner, Paul, 480 Redwood Street, Suite 10, Vallejo CA, 94590 (707) 643-3687 


